Sep 9, 2019 - Gabriella Zanna Vanessa Anstruther-Gough-Calthorpe (born 4/8/89), better known by her stage name Gabriella Wilde or Gabriella Calthorpe, is an English model & actress who has appeared in The Three Musketeers (2011), Carrie (2013), & Endless Love (2014). She is descended from the aristocratic Gough-Calthorpe family. Wilde began her career as a model, spotted at age 14 by Naomi Campbell. Wilde is engaged to musician Alan Pownall. The couple's first son, Sasha Blue Pownall, was born 2/3/14.
. See more ideas about gabriella wilde, model, carrie 2013.
